      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c448-102">使用<xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別，以在啟動視窗中，顯示的影像或*啟動顯示畫面*、 WPF 應用程式啟動時。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-102">Use the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class to show an image in a startup window, or *splash screen*, when a WPF application starts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-103">呼叫<xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Show%2A>方法，以顯示啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-103">Call the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Show%2A> method to display the splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-104">呼叫<xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Close%2A>關閉啟動顯示畫面的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-104">Call the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen.Close%2A> method to close the splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-105">指定要用於映像<xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-105">Specify the image to use in the <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c448-106"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別可以顯示任何支援 Windows Imaging Component (WIC) 的映像格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-106">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class can display any image format that is supported by the Windows Imaging Component (WIC).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-107">例如，您可以使用 BMP、 GIF、 JPEG、 PNG 或 TIFF 格式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-107">For example, you can use the BMP, GIF, JPEG, PNG, or TIFF format.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-108">如果影像是 PNG 檔案，其中包含 alpha 色頻影像會轉譯使用中的 alpha 色頻所定義的透明度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-108">If the image is a PNG file and it includes an alpha channel, the image is rendered using the transparency defined in the alpha channel.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c448-109">您無法在啟動顯示畫面，稍後會加入您的程式碼中包含預留位置文字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-109">You cannot include placeholder text in the splash screen that is later added by your code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-110">如果您想要在啟動顯示畫面中包含文字，您必須將它新增至影像檔。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-110">If you want to include text in the splash screen, you must add it to the image file.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7c448-111">您不需要撰寫任何程式碼，以顯示啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-111">It is not necessary to write any code to display a splash screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-112">從開始[!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)]SP1，您可以快速地設定啟動顯示畫面使用預設設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-112">Starting in [!INCLUDE[vs_orcas_long](~/includes/vs-orcas-long-md.md)] SP1, you can quickly configure a splash screen with default settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-113">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> [ 如何： 在 WPF 應用程式中加入啟動顯示畫面](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-113">For more information, see [How to: Add a Splash Screen to a WPF Application](~/docs/framework/wpf/app-development/how-to-add-a-splash-screen-to-a-wpf-application.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c448-114"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別會顯示啟動顯示畫面的儘速應用程式啟動之後。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-114">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class displays the splash screen as soon as possible after the application is started.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-115">建立 WPF 應用程式執行個體之前，請使用原生程式碼，會顯示啟動顯示畫面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-115">The splash screen is displayed by using native code, before the WPF application instance is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-116">啟動顯示畫面會顯示在螢幕的中央。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-116">The splash screen is displayed in the center of the screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-117">載入應用程式時，啟動顯示畫面會淡入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-117">When the application is loaded, the splash screen fades.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c448-118">當您的應用程式編譯時，映像中內嵌為受管理的資源組件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-118">When your application is compiled, the image is embedded as a managed resource in the assembly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7c448-119">如果當地語系化的應用程式，將映像會內嵌在當地語系化的附屬 DLL 中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-119">If the application is localized, the image is embedded in the localized satellite DLL.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7c448-120"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別不適用於部分信任。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-120">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class is not available in partial trust.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7c448-121"><xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen>類別不能在 XAML 瀏覽器應用程式 (Xbap)，因為它們使用不同的啟動架構。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c448-121">The <xref:System.Windows.SplashScreen> class cannot be used in XAML Browser Applications (XBAPs), because they use a different startup architecture.</span></span>  
  
   
  
